<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script> 
</body>

 34700=<!DOCTYPE HTML> 
<html> 
<body > 
  <div class="logo" style="background-color: #fff; height: 80px;">
  
  </div>
    <p class="main">
		Site is under scheduled maintenance!
	</p>
	<p class="main1">We will be back online at</p>
  
<div id="clockdiv"> 
  <!-- <div> 
    <span class="days" id="day"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Days</div> 
  </div>  -->
  
  <div> 
    <span class="hours" id="hour"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Hours</div> 
  </div> 
  <div> 
    <span class="minutes" id="minute"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Minutes</div> 
  </div> 
  <div> 
    <span class="seconds" id="second"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Seconds</div> 
  </div> 
</div> 
	<p class="headline">
		To serve you better, we're upgrading our systems.
		Your patience is appreciated.
	</p>
    <p class="headline">				
		You can reach us at - <span style="font-weight:bold">sbiepay@sbi.co.in</span>
	</p>
<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script> 
</body> 
<head>

  text-align: center;

}

    padding: 15px; 
    border-radius: 3px; 
    display: inline-block; 
} 
smalltext{ 
    padding-top: 5px; 
    font-size: 16px;

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);

document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;

        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000);

  </div>
    <p class="main">
		Site is under scheduled maintenance!
	</p>
	<p class="main1">We will be back online at</p>
  
<div id="clockdiv"> 
  <!-- <div> 
    <span class="days" id="day"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Days</div> 
  </div>  -->

    <span class="hours" id="hour"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Hours</div> 
  </div> 
  <div> 
    <span class="minutes" id="minute"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Minutes</div> 
  </div> 
  <div> 
    <span class="seconds" id="second"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Seconds</div> 
  </div> 
</div> 
	<p class="headline">
		To serve you better, we're upgrading our systems.
		Your patience is appreciated.
	</p>
    <p class="headline">				
		You can reach us at - <span style="font-weight:bold">sbiepay@sbi.co.in</span>
	</p>
<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script> 
</body> 
<head> 
<style> 
body{ 
  text-align: center; 
/*background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #4facfe , #00f2fe ); */
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-color:#000061;
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-weight: 100; 
  margin: 0 auto;
}

  color: #fff;

    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
}

    padding: 15px; 
    border-radius: 3px; 
    display: inline-block; 
} 
smalltext{ 
    padding-top: 5px; 
    font-size: 16px; 
}

  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 45px;
}

    <span class="days" id="day"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Days</div> 
  </div>  -->
  
  <div> 
    <span class="hours" id="hour"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Hours</div> 
  </div> 
  <div> 
    <span class="minutes" id="minute"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Minutes</div> 
  </div> 
  <div> 
    <span class="seconds" id="second"></span> 
    <div class="smalltext">Seconds</div> 
  </div> 
</div> 
	<p class="headline">
		To serve you better, we're upgrading our systems.
		Your patience is appreciated.
	</p>
    <p class="headline">				
		You can reach us at - <span style="font-weight:bold">sbiepay@sbi.co.in</span>
	</p>
<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script> 
</body> 
<head> 
<style> 
body{ 
  text-align: center; 
/*background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #4facfe , #00f2fe ); */
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-color:#000061;
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-weight: 100; 
  margin: 0 auto;
} 
h1{ 
  color: #fff; 
  font-weight: 100; 
  font-size: 50px; 
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  margin: 40px 0px 20px; 
} 
 #clockdiv{ 
    font-family: sans-serif; 
    color: #fff; 
    display: inline-block; 
    font-weight: 100; 
    text-align: center; 
    font-size: 25px;
	height:150px;	
} 
#clockdiv > div{ 
    padding: 10px; 
    border-radius: 3px; 
    background: #4facfe;
    display: inline-block; 
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
} 
#clockdiv div > span{ 
    padding: 15px; 
    border-radius: 3px; 
    display: inline-block; 
} 
smalltext{ 
    padding-top: 5px; 
    font-size: 16px; 
} 
h1{
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 45px;
}
.main{
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 40px;
  color: #fff;
}
.main1{
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 30px;
  color: #fff;
}
p{
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-size: 23px;
  color: #fff;
}
.headline{
  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: #fff;
  
}

.logo {
	background: url(data:image/png;base64,);
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-position: center;
	height: 65px;
	width: 100%;
}

</style> 
</head>

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script> 
</body>

  text-align: center;

  font-weight: 100; 
  margin: 0 auto;

  </div>  -->

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script> 
</body> 
<head>

  text-align: center;

  font: 20px Helvetica, sans-serif;
  font-weight: 100; 
  margin: 0 auto;

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script>

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script>

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script>

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script>

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script>

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script>

<script> 

var deadline = new Date("February 27 2022 05:00:00").getTime(); 
  
var x = setInterval(function() { 
  
var now = new Date().getTime(); 
var t = deadline - now; 
var days = Math.floor(t / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); 
var hours = Math.floor((t%(1000 * 60 * 60 * 24))/(1000 * 60 * 60)); 
var minutes = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60)); 
var seconds = Math.floor((t % (1000 * 60)) / 1000); 
// document.getElementById("day").innerHTML =days ; 
document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML =hours; 
document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML = minutes;  
document.getElementById("second").innerHTML =seconds;  
if (t < 0) { 
        clearInterval(x); 
        document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = "TIME UP"; 
        // document.getElementById("day").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("hour").innerHTML ='0'; 
        document.getElementById("minute").innerHTML ='0' ;  
        document.getElementById("second").innerHTML = '0'; } 
}, 1000); 
</script> 
</body>
